		}
		{
			dependencies: ["55ACAF8733D01A33"]
			description: [
				"You can now unlock &lCreate&r!"
				""
				"What this means is that you can now make cool contraptions, such as tunnel bores, automatic farms, etc..."
				""
				"However, all processing machines from Create have been &cdeprecated&r in this pack. Their recipes have been fulfilled by GregTech machines, so you can't craft them."
				""
				"{@pagebreak}"
				""
				"I highly advise you to make a cactus farm with the reward I gave you so that you can turn it into lime dye and combine it with dough to make slime balls, which can then be turned into super glue."
			]
			id: "3776E37FEF41654C"
			rewards: [{
				count: 8
