		{
			dependencies: ["61FF5795C584957A"]
			description: [
				"I hope you have saved up a good bit of creosote oil!"
				"If you haven't, then don't worry, you can still just make some... It'll take a while though."
				""
				"Anyways, the Primitive Pump is a multiblock machine made almost entirely out of treated wood. Treated wood requires wood and creosote oil to make. When it's assembled, it'll start creating water!"
				""
				"Then you'll need to bring the water to your boilers with pipes."
			]
			icon: "gtceu:primitive_pump"
