		{
			dependencies: ["78730BBC6D347D48"]
			description: [
				"The reason you are going to the nether is because there are valuable Sulfur veins and netherrack there. You can smelt the sulfur ore to get sulfur, which you can then combine with rubber pulp to get rubber ingots, which you can then turn into rubber plates! You'll need a bit of rubber to unlock &7LV&r, and there you'll need a LOT of rubber to progress, so luckily there's a better recipe with some electric machines."
				""
				"If you can't easily find a sulfur vein then you can use netherrack for a less efficient recipe."
			]
			icon: "gtceu:rubber_plate"
			id: "5FDD97D2EA0ADA28"
			subtitle: "Going to hell and back just for this"
