		{
			dependencies: ["55ACAF8733D01A33"]
			description: [
				"The &lElectron tube&r is like the Vacuum Tube but with less microcrafting. Also, it's used for Create stuff."
				"To make it, you'll need rose quartz, which you need to make in an alloy smelter with 8 redstone and 1 nether quartz. Then, you'll need some sand paper. Hold the sand paper in your offhand and the rose quartz in your main hand and hold right click to polish the quartz."
